hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實大把人為嫁而嫁啦<br />\n但至少依家黎姿幸福咪得<br />\n學下祝福人得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4f011e94d875a95cd4c314a7f769e157baf24e","tid":872951,"uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b2bc12e157ed5bff33c5ef30596277b642c03773","tid":872951,"uid":34777,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"屌你地樓上班撚樣<br />\n把口咪咁臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎姿個人咁顧家咁有能力都要俾連登仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實大把人為嫁而嫁啦<br />\n但至少依家黎姿幸福咪得<br />\n學下祝福人得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/69452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F69452&d=sQ4YyRmqG3u9s5iFVk398P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4aed1ad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/69452</a><br />\n睇完依篇報導，覺得佢老公真係對佢好好，個細佬呢十年嚟既醫藥洗費咁大，佢老公都肯無上限泵水比佢。雖然係有錢佬，但係如果我係佢老公既話，真係會簡玩吓女過日子就算，唔會娶佢嚟做老婆仲幫佢養埋個細佬。"},{"pid":"73ea5f1637a6b8cdc674581801ba2d6ea3fe39bb","tid":872951,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f59eefeb20f39058a0734306599704eab5690e","tid":872951,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ff47651f39fd7eaeb61bb1bcf65b38a8d593fbcc","tid":872951,"uid":106426,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"就係貪佢有經驗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d42638c6c13c876bf2c00bc54bd697a0687d465","tid":872951,"uid":172306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"點解一定要帶黑超 係有冇咩原因"},{"pid":"a013fc4e0e58a14d852a55cd22bc9fd2fc38dd4f","tid":872951,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"扶住都話企..."},{"pid":"c2b6609b1e8119fa764c0503ea9576a80b79790e","tid":872951,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a013fc4e0e58a14d852a55cd22bc9fd2fc38dd4f","tid":872951,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"扶住都話企..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"好叻架啦...<br />\n唔好咁挑剔啦"},{"pid":"30eb53d70c73d739a31d0d9255d22953ed4df510","tid":872951,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de79e9ffbf89ba4e60de299e33048800c0ca028d","tid":872951,"uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"273cca5c2655c5750fe3b3befe437410c87bccb5","tid":872951,"uid":206899,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"似扶老豆多過扶細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm